    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the study we test whether transcranial direct current stimulation can reduce the
      perception of pain in patients with chronic inflammatory bowel diseases.

      Hypothesis: Transcranial direct current stimulation can reduce the perception of pain in
      patients with chronic inflammatory bowel diseases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
